            <p>And that is why we have curtains! To save us from that kind of torture of having to wake up early on a Sunday morning just because the sun decided to glow a little too brightly. Not just that though! Curtains help accent the beauty of your rooms you spent time and energy on designing. And oh, it can also save you from the eyes of a creepy peeping Tom!</p>

